      • publishNewUserEvent

        public void publishNewUserEvent(User accountCreator,
                                java.util.List admins,
                                java.lang.String domain,
                                java.lang.String password)
        Publishes a new user event to the message queue
        Parameters:
        accountCreator - The person whom created the user
        admins - Org admins
        domain - The servername for this server (used to build url).
        password - The user's password. It must be explicitly passed in seperate from the user because the password associated with the User object might be encrypted, thus useless for this method
